 src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d723a598f589d59972884e1c3be32b5053bdddab","tid":2142272,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T11:10:27.000Z","msg":"12歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}